bezoss-ex-wife-mackenzie-scott-is-still-worth-33-billion-after-giving-away-10-million-a-day-for-seven-years-but-she-once-worked-as-a-dishwasher-and-waitress-earning-minimum-wage-of-4-25-an-hour/articleshow/132365750.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/jeff-bezoss-ex-wife-mackenzie-scott-is-still-worth-33-billion-after-giving-away-10-million-a-day-for-seven-years-but-she-once-worked-as-a-dishwasher-and-waitress-earning-minimum-wage-of-4-25-an-hour/articleshow/132365750.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-13T18:23:27+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132367390,imgsize-131878.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Get ready for sudden death': Iran media's Lindsey Graham reference in warning to Trump, Netanyahu]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132366341.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iranian newspapers featured Senator Lindsey Graham's death on their front pages. Some publications issued veiled warnings directed at the US and its leaders. One newspaper described Graham as the "Merchant of Death" following his sudden illness. State media celebrated his passing, calling him "sent to hell." These remarks fueled speculation among some supporters of President Trump's movement.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/get-ready-for-sudden-death-iran-medias-lindsey-graham-reference-in-warning-to-trump-netanyahu/articleshow/132366341.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/get-ready-for-sudden-death-iran-medias-lindsey-graham-reference-in-warning-to-trump-netanyahu/articleshow/132366341.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-13T17:53:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="im