ure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132366003,imgsize-37468.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Snoop Dogg: ‘You can take your boy out the hood but you can't take the hood out the homie’]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132364140.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The influence of our surroundings extends far beyond mere memories, deeply embedding in our character and daily behaviors. Our formative settings mold not only our speech and desires but also our fundamental instincts. Even as we advance in life, these early lessons remain pivotal, guiding our perceptions and interactions. This ongoing relationship underscores the importance of integrating past experiences as we navigate new paths in life.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-snoop-dogg-you-can-take-your-boy-out-the-hood-but-you-cant-take-the-hood-out-the-homie/articleshow/132364140.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-snoop-dogg-you-can-take-your-boy-out-the-hood-but-you-cant-take-the-hood-out-the-homie/articleshow/132364140.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-13T18:00:00+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132364539,imgsize-143702.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Confucius: 'The superior man is modest in his speech, but exceeds in his actions']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132364664.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Confucius emphasized that true character is reflected in consistent actions rather than mere words. His teachings prioritized personal integrity and the moral growth of individuals over social status. He believed that lasting stability relies on the moral behavior of individuals, particularly leaders. In today's world, talk often overshadows action, yet real value shines through achievements rather than just declarations.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/quote-of-the-day-by-confucius-the-superior-man-is-modest-in-his-speech-but-exceeds-in-his-actions/articleshow/132364664.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/quote-of-the-day-by-confucius-the-superior-man-is-modest-in-his-speech-but-exceeds-in-his-actions/articleshow/132364664.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-13T17:00:00+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132364806,imgsize-120967.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ocean warming has been shrinking marine animals for 450 million years, massive study reveals]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132365086.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/ocean-warming-has-been-shrinking-marine-animals-for-450-million-years-massive-study-reveals/articleshow/132365086.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/ocean-warming-has-been-shrinking-marine-animals-for-450-million-years-massive-study-reveals/articleshow/132365086.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-13T16:37:51+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132365094,imgsize-2067771.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Buried for 5,300 years beneath a Stone Age tomb, a skull discovered in Spain has revealed the world's earliest known ear surgery]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132364589.cms" 